43:43.443 --> 43:46.254
♪ The journey of youth has no end ♪

43:46.254 --> 43:48.316
♪ Year by year ♪

43:49.256 --> 43:52.345
♪ Rain will pass by your window ♪

43:52.345 --> 43:54.748
♪ Then run towards the sunny day ♪

43:55.080 --> 43:57.960
♪ Dreams await at the start
of our encounter ♪

43:57.960 --> 44:00.188
♪ Touching the fingertips ♪

44:00.936 --> 44:04.008
♪ Longing for the world in your eyes ♪

44:04.008 --> 44:07.240
♪ The unspoken understanding
reflects in our gaze ♪

44:07.240 --> 44:08.616
♪ You smile ♪

44:08.616 --> 44:11.996
♪ And get a little closer to me ♪

44:13.032 --> 44:15.172
♪ I want to go with you ♪

44:15.172 --> 44:18.118
♪ To a farther future ♪

44:18.118 --> 44:20.552
♪ Dreams can reach the other shore ♪

44:20.552 --> 44:23.926
♪ I really like you a lot ♪

44:23.926 --> 44:27.016
♪ The first time I am brave ♪

44:27.016 --> 44:30.803
♪ Looking up,
chasing the momentary fireworks ♪

44:30.803 --> 44:32.456
♪ Falling in the midst of summer ♪

44:32.456 --> 44:33.832
♪ Every moment of falling in love ♪

44:33.832 --> 44:36.860
